1. *Razumiješ* li šta ti govorim? (Do you understand what I'm telling you?)
2. Ona *razumije* sve što mu govori. (She understands everything he is saying.)
3. Znaš da ja *razumijem* tebe. (You know I understand you.)
4. Oni sada *razumiju* da je to pogrešno. (They now understand that it is wrong.)
5. *Razumijemo* se bez riječi. (We understand each other without words.)